== Install dependencies ==
- libSDL 1.2
- SDL_mixer 1.2
On gentoo:
$ emerge -av libsdl sdl-mixer
On debian/ubuntu:
$ aptitude install libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-mixer1.2-dev

== Compile twin-e ==
% cd src
% make
$ make install

== Copy datas from LBA ==
% cd ../bin
% mkdir -p data
% cp -R <PLACE WHERE THE GAME IS>/* data

== Run twin-e ==
% ./twin-e


